<map version="1.0.0"><node Text="思维导图"><node ID="A41CB437-6455-4523-B7B0-771B12750233" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="MVC" COLOR="#164355" POSITION="right" STYLE="bubble"><edge COLOR="#FFFFFF" WIDTH="2" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue-Light" SIZE="24" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>从</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> View </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>开始，当用户在</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> UI </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>上进行操作之后，用户的操作被转发到了</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Controller </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>上，</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '>Controller </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>根据用户的操作对数据进行更新</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>(准确来说是调用</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>层的</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> API</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>)，数据更新之后自然视图</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> View </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>展现的内容也需要进行更新。</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '>Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>层此时可以向所有关联的视图发出通知，收到通知的视图重新获取最新的数据。注意这最后一步</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>与</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> View </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>的交互，大部分现有的</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> MVC </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>框架将其进行了封装，开发人员只要使用数据绑定即可。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<node ID="45AF297E-F86F-45DF-9E96-4CA2F793043F" TEXT="&#27010;&#24565;" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#1286DE" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="18" /><node ID="248C4B56-5EBB-4D44-8A72-D0B7A1523749" TEXT="Model" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#1286DE" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '>Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>应该被更准确的称为</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Domain Model</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>(领域模型)，它不代表具体的</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Class </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>或者</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Object</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>，也不是单纯的</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> databse</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>。而是一个</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>“层”</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>的概念：数据在</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>里得到存储，</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '>Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>提供方法操作数据</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>(</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '>Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>的行为)。所以</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Helvetica"; '> Model </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 16px "Times"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Times-Roman"; '>代码可以有业务逻辑，甚至可以有数据的存储操作的底层服务代码。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
