<body><p><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>View</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>、</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Model</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>、</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Controller </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>是</span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> 1:1:1 </span><span style='color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1.000000); font: 18px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>的关系是一种理想状态。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
